title: Ich bin ein Star – Holt mich hier raus!
resume: A batch of more or less known celebrities, ready to expose themselves to a large amount of viewers, have to spend about two weeks in an Australian jungle camp. Each day, the viewers vote for the celebrity they would like to face a difficult task and later vote for their favorite to become the “Queen” or “King of the Jungle”.  Based on the British reality television show I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!
